.ralph/runs/run-20260413-004018-509304-iter-1.log:277:      "title": "Prioritize defensive next action",
.ralph/runs/run-20260413-004018-509304-iter-1.log:278:      "description": "Create a simple prioritization model that converts raw findings or observations into one bounded defensive action per iteration. The model should favor actions that reduce real exposure quickly and avoid noisy or low-impact work.",
.ralph/runs/run-20260413-004018-509304-iter-1.log:280:        "The system can rank candidate defensive actions using explicit factors such as severity, exploitability, exposure, confidence, and implementation safety.",
.ralph/runs/run-20260413-004018-509304-iter-1.log:281:        "The loop selects exactly one primary action for the iteration and records why alternatives were not chosen.",
