.ralph/runs/run-20260413-004018-509304-iter-1.log:296:        "The loop defines how to verify the action completed successfully without broadening scope.",
.ralph/runs/run-20260413-004018-509304-iter-1.log:297:        "Unsafe or ambiguous actions are blocked and recorded instead of executed.",
